OL,3,CFire devastates family run hotel in
OL,4,Cthe Gower
OL,6,FA fire has left a family-run hotel in
OL,7,Fthe Gower devastated.
OL,9,FThe roof of the Worms Head Hotel in
OL,10,FRhossili collapsed after a fire broke
OL,11,Fout in the early hours of 14 July.
OL,13,FThe Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService crews from Reynoldston,
OL,15,FSwansea West, Port Talbot, Morriston,
OL,16,FSwansea Central and Gorseinon Fire
OL,17,FStations attended the scene along with
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police.
