OL,3,CFire devastates family run hotel in
OL,4,Cthe Gower
OL,6,FThe spokesperson for Mid and West
OL,7,FWales Fire and Rescue Service said,
OL,8,F"Crews responded to a fire within the
OL,9,Fproperty's accommodation block, which
OL,10,Fspread to the block's entire roof
OL,11,Fspace."
OL,13,F"No casualties were reported and all
OL,14,Foccupants were accounted for."
OL,16,F"The property has been significantly
OL,17,Fdamaged by the fire. The cause of the
OL,18,Ffire has not yet been identified."
