OL,3,CFire devastates family run hotel in
OL,4,Cthe Gower
OL,6,FThe fire was extinguished at around
OL,7,F5:30am with the last crews leaving
OL,8,Fjust after 9:30am.
OL,10,FThe hotel's owner said "It is
OL,11,Fparticularly heartbreaking and soul-
OL,12,Fdestroying for me and family to see 25
OL,13,Fyears of hard work destroyed in less
OL,14,Fthan 30 minutes. "
OL,16,F"Not sure how we come back from this
OL,17,Fat all let alone in the near term
OL,18,Ffuture but we will strive to come back
OL,19,Fstronger."
